  "intent_precise": "BP Genomics RNA Extraction: Using magplate (plate, slot NEST 1mL Deep Well Plate), Elution Plate (pcr_plate, slot 1), Liquid Waste (reservoir, slot 8), Trough with Reagents (labware, slot 2). With magnetic module. (1) Pause: Out of 20ul tips. Please replace in slot 3. (2) Pause: Out of 1000ul tips. Please replace in slot 6. (3) Distribute 580\u00b5L from source A1 to destination wells A1. (4) Incubate for 5 minutes. (5) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (6) Incubate for 6 minutes. (7) Transfer from source to destination. (8) Disengage magnets to release beads. (9) Transfer from source A1 to destination A1. (10) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (11) Incubate for 5 minutes. (12) Disengage magnets to release beads. (13) Incubate for 10 minutes. (14) Consolidate 20\u00b5L from source wells A1, A1, A1 into destination A1. (15) Incubate for 2 minutes. (16) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (17) Incubate for 2 minutes. (18) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (19) Disengage magnets to release beads.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform distribute to A1, sample consolidation, magnetic bead separation. (volumes 1\u00b5L-800\u00b5L, ~32 min total)",
  "intent": "For this BP Genomics RNA extraction, you'll need to set up your magplate in the NEST 1mL Deep Well Plate slot, PCR elution plate in slot 1, liquid waste reservoir in slot 8, and reagent trough in slot 2 - make sure to replace the 20\u00b5L tips in slot 3 and 1000\u00b5L tips in slot 6 when prompted. Start by distributing 580\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1, then incubate for 5 minutes before engaging the magnets at magheightmm height for 6 minutes of bead separation. You'll cycle through several rounds of magnetic separation with 5-minute captures and 10-minute incubations, then finish by consolidating 20\u00b5L from three A1 source wells into destination A1, followed by a final 2-minute magnetic separation at magheightmm height before transferring 20\u00b5L to the final destination A1.",
